Class ErrWorldFile

java.lang.Object
  com.bbn.openmap.dataAccess.image.WorldFile
      com.bbn.openmap.dataAccess.image.ErrWorldFile

public class ErrWorldFile
extends WorldFile

An ErrWorldFile is a World File that can't be handled for some reason. This class is used as a placeholder to let an ImageReader know there is some problem figuring out where or how to locate the associated image file.
